## F16 Sprint 1 — Done

**What was done:**

The two route files (`src/app/api/seed/route.ts` and `src/app/api/seed/status/route.ts`) already existed from F15 and were correct against the spec. The sprint work was writing the unit tests:

**Tests written:**

- `src/app/api/seed/__tests__/route.test.ts` — mocks `@/lib/seed`; covers 201 success (ok/events/users), 500 on Error, 500 on non-Error
- `src/app/api/seed/status/__tests__/route.test.ts` — mocks `@/lib/clickhouse`; covers 200 with numeric values, string→number conversion, zero counts, 500 on Error, 500 on non-Error

**One notable fix:** the failure tests initially used `vi.clearAllMocks()` before setting up rejections, but that doesn't flush the `mockResolvedValueOnce` queue from `beforeEach`. Switched to `mockQuery.mockReset()` so `Promise.all` correctly sees the rejection on its first call.

**Sprint contract results:** test 248/248 ✅ | lint warnings only (pre-existing) ✅ | typecheck ✅ | build ✅ | all file criteria ✅
